Package: CNVgears
Type: Package
Title: A Framework of Functions to Combine, Analize and Interpret CNVs Calling Results 
Version: 0.4.0
Author: Simone Montalbano
Maintainer: Simone Montalbano <simone.montalbano@protonmail.com>
Description: This package contains a set of functions to perform several type of 
    processing and analysis on CNVs calling pipelines/algorithms results in an 
    inegrated manner and regardless of the raw data type (SNPs array or NGS).
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    ggplot2
Suggests:
    VariantAnnotation,
    DelayedArray,
    knitr,
    biomaRt,
    evobiR,
    rmarkdown,
    devtools,
    cowplot,
    usethis,
    scales
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
